name: Better Photoshop Techniques magazine
overview:
Better Photoshop Techniques is a special interest magazine published by Better Publishing Pty Ltd, ABN 77 115 047 688, P.O. Box 5455, Chittaway Bay, NSW, Australia.

Better Photoshop Techniques is printed by Toppan Printing Pty Ltd, Hong Kong, ACN 001 239 210; and is distributed in Australia and New Zealand by Network Distribution Company. All visual content, design and layout created in Adobe Photoshop and Adobe InDesign.
